---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const lastUpdated = '2026-05-23';
---

<BaseLayout title="Now — Corey Juarez" description="What I'm up to right now.">
    <div class="max-w-xl">
        <div class="mb-12 flex items-baseline justify-between border-b border-main pb-4">
            <h1 class="font-serif text-2xl font-medium">Now</h1>
            <p class="font-mono text-xs text-muted">Updated {lastUpdated}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-10 font-serif text-lg leading-relaxed">
            <section>
                <h2 class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-muted mb-4">Work</h2>
                <p>
                    Heads-down on a propulsion project at work — real hardware, real deadlines. The kind of
                    thing where the simulation is never quite right and you end up learning more from the
                    failure than the success.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-muted mb-4">The Boat</h2>
                <p>
                    Deep into the sailboat refit. Currently working through the electrical system — which
                    means spending a lot of time in the bilge with a headlamp and a multimeter. Progress is
                    slow but the end is starting to look real.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-muted mb-4">Reading</h2>
                <p>
                    <em>The Soul of a New Machine</em> by Tracy Kidder. Should have read it years ago.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-muted mb-4">Writing</h2>
                <p>
                    Working on a piece about what the van build taught me about constraints — how a tight
                    budget and 80 square feet forced better decisions than an open checkbook would have.
                </p>
            </section>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-16 font-mono text-xs text-muted">
            This is a <a href="https://nownownow.com/about" class="underline decoration-dashed underline-offset-2 hover:text-accent hover:decoration-solid transition-colors">/now page</a>.
            Everyone should have one.
        </p>
    </div>
</BaseLayout>
